title: Syrian green beans with tomatoes
ingredients: ['3 tablespoons olive oil', '1 small onion, minced', '1 garlic clove, minced', '1 tablespoon cumin spice mix', '300g green beans, trimmed', '1 (400g) tin chopped tomatoes', '1 tablespoon tomato puree', '1/2 teaspoon salt', 'extra virgin olive oil for drizzling']
